<card id="howtoplay" title="How to play">
<p>
The rules of Sudoku are simple: 
</p>
<p>
Simply fill in the grid so that every row, column and 3x3 box contain the numbers 1 to 9.
</p>
<p><b>Remember:</b> each number should appear only once in any row, column or 3x3 box.
</p>
<p>
