<card id="controls" title="Game controls">
<p>
<b>To move the cursor:</b> use your phone's keypad or joystick.
</p>
<p>
<b>To enter a number:</b> choose "MARK" and press the number you wish to enter on your phone's keypad.
</p>
<p>
<b>To erase a number:</b> choose "MARK" and press the 0 key on your phone's keypad.
</p>
